          "_nested_name": "home_practice_challenges.text_challenge_3"
        },
        {
          "name": "reply_challenge_3",
          "value": "Can you make a consequence for if this happens again? When we establish a consequence together with our teens, the consequence will be more realistic, and our teens will be more willing and able to follow the rule.",
